2. the indian is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is the writer##1
4. the fan of house is on the far left##1
5. the fan of house is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2       |
